title: trace - MediationZone Documentation 9.3 - InfoZone
text: usage: trace <command> This command can be used for starting a Conditional Trace trace if you have the Jaeger exporter running. Return Codes Listed below are the different return codes for the trace command: Code Description Code Description 0 Will be returned if the command was successful. 1 Will be returned if the syntax is incorrect. 4 Will be returned if errors occur during execution of the command.
